Invocation Name: doctor kishore
des: Dr. Kishore is a psychiatrist based in Albany NY, who provides treatment for emotional and psychiatric problems. This skill will help you learn about Dr. Kishore's office address, directions, office hours and the list of Insurances that he accepts. To get started with the skill, search for "doctor kishore" in the Alexa skill store and then "enable" the skill. Say Alexa Launch or Open Doctor Kishore to get started. You can also get info at http://drkishore.com.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
